    // Patterns -> ko smajhone se liye, aapko basic se start karna hoga. Aapko C++ ke syntax aur basic concepts ko samajhna hoga. Jaise ki variables, data types, operators, control structures (if-else, loops), functions, arrays, pointers, etc. Aapko in concepts ko practice karna hoga, taaki aap unhe achhi tarah se samajh sake. Aapko chhote chhote programs likhne honge, jisse aapko in concepts ko apply karne ka mauka milega. Aapko apne code ko step by step likhna hoga, aur har step ko samajhne ki koshish karni hogi. Aapko apne code ko debug karne ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne mistakes ko samajh sake aur unhe sudhar sake. Aapko apne code ko optimize karne ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko efficient bana sake. Aapko apne code ko modular banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko reuse kar sake aur maintain kar sake. Aapko apne code ko document karne ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko samajhne me asani ho aur dusre log bhi aapke code ko samajh sake. Aapko apne code ko version control system (like Git) me rakhne ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ke changes ko track kar sake aur apne code ko collaborate kar sake. Aapko apne code ko test karne ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ke functionality ko verify kar sake aur apne code me bugs ko identify kar sake. Aapko apne code ko refactor karne ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko improve kar sake aur apne code ko maintainable bana sake. Aapko apne code ko secure banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko vulnerabilities se bachaye aur apne code ko safe banaye. Aapko apne code ko performance optimize karne ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko fast bana sake aur apne code ke resource usage ko minimize kar sake. Aapko apne code ko scalable banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko large scale applications me use kar sake aur apne code ko future proof bana sake. Aapko apne code ko maintainable banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko easily update kar sake aur apne code ko long term me use kar sake. Aapko apne code ko readable banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko easily understand kar sake aur apne code ko dusre log bhi easily samajh sake. Aapko apne code ko consistent banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko easily read kar sake aur apne code ko dusre log bhi easily samajh sake. Aapko apne code ko modular banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko easily reuse kar sake aur apne code ko maintain kar sake. Aapko apne code ko testable banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko easily test kar sake aur apne code me bugs ko identify kar sake. Aapko apne code ko secure banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko vulnerabilities se bachaye aur apne code ko safe banaye. Aapko apne code ko performance optimize karne ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko fast bana sake aur apne code ke resource usage ko minimize kar sake. Aapko apne code ko scalable banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko large scale applications me use kar sake aur apne code ko future proof bana sake. Aapko apne code ko maintainable banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko easily update kar sake aur apne code ko long term me use kar sake. Aapko apne code ko readable banane ki bhi practice karni hogi, taaki aap apne code ko easily understand kar sake aur apne code ko dusre log bhi easily samajh sake.

